      <section id="how" aria-labelledby="how-heading">
        <div class="container">
          <span class="section-label">How it works</span>
          <h2 id="how-heading" style="font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem); color: var(--warm-gray-9); margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px;">
            Three primitives. One artifact.
          </h2>
          <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--warm-gray-5); max-width: 520px;">
            Author once. Compose into flows. Ship as a bundle. Consumers stay in sync automatically.
          </p>
          <div class="steps">

            <!-- Step 1: Blocks -->
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-number" aria-hidden="true">1</div>
              <h3>Build reusable API Blocks</h3>
              <p>Each block is a typed HTTP request template — inputs, URL, headers, body with <code>&#123;&#123;token&#125;&#125;</code> interpolation, and JSONPath output extractors.</p>
              <div class="step-diagram" aria-label="API Block diagram">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 260 140" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="An API block with inputs, request, and outputs">
                  <!-- Block card -->
                  <rect x="20" y="16" width="220" height="108" rx="10" fill="white" stroke="#e8e4d8" stroke-width="1"/>
                  <!-- Header -->
                  <rect x="20" y="16" width="220" height="32" rx="10" fill="#6741d9"/>
                  <rect x="20" y="36" width="220" height="12" fill="#6741d9"/>
                  <text x="36" y="36" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="11" fill="white" font-weight="600">POST /payments/charge</text>
                  <!-- Inputs row -->
                  <text x="36" y="65" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="9" fill="#7c766a" font-weight="600" letter-spacing="0.04em">INPUTS</text>
                  <rect x="36" y="72" width="60" height="18" rx="4" fill="#f3f1ea" stroke="#d6d1c2" stroke-width="1"/>
                  <text x="42" y="84" font-family="var(--font-mono), monospace" font-size="8.5" fill="#5c564c">amount</text>
                  <rect x="104" y="72" width="60" height="18" rx="4" fill="#f3f1ea" stroke="#d6d1c2" stroke-width="1"/>
                  <text x="110" y="84" font-family="var(--font-mono), monospace" font-size="8.5" fill="#5c564c">currency</text>
                  <!-- Output row -->
                  <text x="36" y="107" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="9" fill="#7c766a" font-weight="600" letter-spacing="0.04em">OUTPUT</text>
                  <rect x="80" y="98" width="80" height="18" rx="4" fill="#e6fcf5" stroke="#96f2d7" stroke-width="1"/>
                  <text x="86" y="110" font-family="var(--font-mono), monospace" font-size="8.5" fill="#099268">$.charge_id</text>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 2: Scenarios -->
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-number" aria-hidden="true">2</div>
              <h3>Compose into Scenarios</h3>
              <p>Chain blocks linearly or use the visual graph editor for branching flows. Pass context between steps. Embed scenarios inside scenarios for reuse.</p>
              <div class="step-diagram" aria-label="Scenario flow diagram">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 260 140" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="Three blocks connected in a flow with a branch">
                  <!-- Block 1 -->
                  <rect x="16" y="56" width="64" height="28" rx="6" fill="#f3f0ff" stroke="#b197fc" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                  <text x="48" y="73" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="9" fill="#6741d9" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">Auth Token</text>
                  <!-- Arrow 1 -->
                  <line x1="80" y1="70" x2="100" y2="70" stroke="#b197fc" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                  <polygon points="100,66 108,70 100,74" fill="#b197fc"/>
                  <!-- Block 2 -->
                  <rect x="108" y="56" width="64" height="28" rx="6" fill="#f3f0ff" stroke="#b197fc" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                  <text x="140" y="73" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="9" fill="#6741d9" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">Charge</text>
                  <!-- Branch lines -->
                  <line x1="172" y1="70" x2="188" y2="50" stroke="#0ca678" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4,3"/>
                  <line x1="172" y1="70" x2="188" y2="96" stroke="#e03e52" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="4,3"/>
                  <!-- ok block -->
                  <rect x="188" y="36" width="56" height="24" rx="5" fill="#e6fcf5" stroke="#96f2d7" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                  <text x="216" y="51" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="8.5" fill="#099268" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">Receipt</text>
                  <!-- error block -->
                  <rect x="188" y="84" width="56" height="24" rx="5" fill="#fff0f0" stroke="#ffc9c9" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                  <text x="216" y="99" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="8.5" fill="#c92a2a" font-weight="600" text-anchor="middle">Retry</text>
                  <!-- ok/error labels -->
                  <text x="183" y="46" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="7.5" fill="#0ca678" font-weight="700">ok</text>
                  <text x="178" y="99" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="7.5" fill="#c92a2a" font-weight="700">error</text>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 3: Bundle -->
            <div class="step">
              <div class="step-number" aria-hidden="true">3</div>
              <h3>Ship as a signed Bundle</h3>
              <p>Export your entire project — all versions, all flows, all environments — as one <code>.json</code> file. Consumers import it, switch versions in one click, see explicit diffs.</p>
              <div class="step-diagram" aria-label="Bundle artifact diagram">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 260 140" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="A signed JSON bundle with version history">
